    :hasInteractionDescription "Sulfamethoxazole and other sulfonamides may potentiate the effects of some drugs, such as oral anticoagulants, methotrexate, and phenytoin; this may be due to displacement of the drug from plasma protein binding sites or to inhibition of metabolism." ;
    :hasManagementAdvice "Not Specified" ;
