        :R118 ;
    :hasSideEffectDescription "Fever, headache, tiredness, weight loss, aches and pains." .

:SE464 a :ErythemaMultiforme ;
    rdfs:label "Erythema multiforme" ;
    :hasDurationOf "Not Specified" ;
    :hasPattern :Not_Specified ;
    :hasReference :R093,
        :R119 ;
    :hasSideEffectDescription "A red to purple rash that causes your skin to puff up (swell) and be painful to the touch.; Pimple-like blisters on your skin or inside of your mouth.; Round mark on your skin that looks like a bulls-eye on a target, with a dark center and a pale ring around it.; Itchy skin." .

:SE465 a :StevensJohnsonSyndrome ;
    rdfs:label "Stevens-Johnson Syndrome" ;
    :hasDurationOf "Not Specified" ;
    :hasPattern :Not_Specified ;
    :hasReference :R093,
        :R120 ;
    :hasSideEffectDescription "Fever, sore mouth and throat, fatigue, burning eyes, unexplained widespread skin pain, red or purple rash that spreads, blisters on your skin and the mucous membranes of the mouth, nose, eyes and genitals, shedding of skin within days after blisters form" .

:SE466 a :ToxicEpidermalNecrolysis ;
    rdfs:label "Toxic epidermal necrolysis" ;
    :hasDurationOf "Not Specified" ;
    :hasPattern :Not_Specified ;
    :hasReference :R093,
        :R121 ;
    :hasSideEffectDescription "It causes peeling and blistering skin over much of the body, including the mouth, eyes, and genitals." .

:SE468 a :Anaphylaxis ;
    rdfs:label "anaphylaxis" ;
    :hasDurationOf "Not Specified" ;
    :hasPattern :Not_Specified ;
    :hasReference :R093,
        :R122 ;
    :hasSideEffectDescription "skin reactions, including hives and itching and flushed or pale skin; low blood pressure (hypotension); constriction of the airways and a swollen tongue or throat, which can cause wheezing and trouble breathing; a weak and rapid pulse; nausea, vomiting or diarrhea; dizziness or fainting" .

:SE469 a :Tremor ;
    rdfs:label "Tremor" ;
    :hasDurationOf "Not Specified" ;
    :hasPattern :Not_Specified ;
    :hasReference :R093,
        :R123 ;
    :hasSideEffectDescription "type of body movement that’s out of your control. It looks like shakiness and can affect many different body parts." .

:SE470 a :Drowsiness ;
    rdfs:label "Drowsiness" ;
    :hasDurationOf "Not Specified" ;
    :hasPattern :Not_Specified ;
    :hasReference :R093 ;
    :hasSideEffectDescription "feeling tired and wanting to fall asleep" .

:SE471 a :Insomnia ;
    rdfs:label "Insomnia" ;
    :hasDurationOf "Not Specified" ;
    :hasPattern :Not_Specified ;
    :hasReference :R093,
        :R124 ;
    :hasSideEffectDescription "Trouble falling asleep; waking up in the middle of the night but falling back asleep; waking up too early without being able to fall back asleep; feeling tired, unwell or sleepy; delayed responses, such as reacting too slowly when you’re driving; Memory issues; Slowed thinking, confusion or trouble concentrating; Mood changes, like anxiety, depression and irritability" .

:SE472 a :Agitation ;
