:SP159 a :AdministrationAndAdherence ;
    rdfs:label "SP159" ;
    :hasReference :R157 ;
    :hasStewardshipDescription "Only take nitrofurantoin if a healthcare provider confirms or strongly suspects a urinary tract infection. Avoid using it for viral infections or other conditions where it won't help, to prevent antibiotic resistance and side effects." .

